fulltitle: Douglas Valentine: Expectations for PBS/Ken Burns' "The Vietnam War" (2017)
title: Douglas Valentine: Expectations for PBS/Ken Burns' "The Vietnam War" (2017)
_filename: _Douglas Valentine - Expectations for PBS_Ken Burns' 'The Vietnam War' (2017).mp4
description:
Spoke with Doug Valentine about the upcoming 10-part Ken Burns documentary "The Vietnam War" (the series begins on Sunday, Sept. 17th, 2017). Doug is an important critical voice about the history of the war and is the author of an important book on the CIA's War in Vietnam called 'the Phoenix Program' and another called 'The CIA as Organized Crime'.

Doug's website: http://douglasvalentine.com

Doug's books
The Phoenix Program: https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00KGMIW6Q/ref=dp-kindle-redirect?_encoding=UTF8&btkr=1
The CIA as Organized Crime:
https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01NAPBE60/ref=dp-kindle-redirect?_encoding=UTF8&btkr=1

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
